channel.title: Ive portforwarded alredy but still no one can connect isit my firewall?
channel.description:
ok so I got all my stuff setup and working but im the only one who can connect, ive portforwarded and everything ive been to [url=http://portforward.com]portforward.com[/url]
and still cannot find the right guide well i found one but i dont know what type of game a server runs off of theres a list of about 600 at portforward.com
if someone would please help i have a [size=15pt]netgear WGR614v6 router[/size]
if you could give a link to a guide for this or simply post how to do it here is an outlook of my router page
note: it dosent have applacations and gaming
[URL=http://img241.imageshack.us/my.php?image=wgr614v62lb7.jpg][IMG]http://img241.imageshack.us/img241/2715/wgr614v62lb7.th.jpg[/img][/URL][URL=http://g.imageshack.us/thpix.php][IMG]http://img241.imageshack.us/images/thpix.gif[/img][/URL] "click to enlarge"
this is the page i get when i go to portforwarding/port-triggering.
[URL=http://img410.imageshack.us/my.php?image=wgr614v64tx3.jpg][IMG]http://img410.imageshack.us/img410/3815/wgr614v64tx3.th.jpg[/img][/URL][URL=http://g.imageshack.us/thpix.php][IMG]http://img410.imageshack.us/images/thpix.gif[/img][/URL] "click to enlarge"
IF YOU KNOW HOW TO PORTFORWARD FOR A [size=15pt]netgear WGR614v6 router[/size]
PLEASE POST HOW TO! THANK YOU FOR READING THIS. HAVE A GREAT DAY!
nickscape
